Description: Optional applications installer
 GNOME application installer for managing Flatpak and Debian package
 installations. Built with TypeScript, GTK4, and Libadwaita.
 .
 Features:
  - Flatpak application management
  - Debian package installation
  - Category-based organization
  - Modern GNOME interface
